    <!-- Key insight callout -->
    <mxCell id="insight" value="💡  Agent never sees the real COOLIFY_API_TOKEN.&#xa;It only holds alp_proxy_jit_aaa — which:&#xa;• only works through the Runner proxy&#xa;• expires when the Job ends&#xa;• is scoped to the declared service + labels" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
